{"tid":1188404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【3歲孫遭滾水淋】心急爺爺幫除衫變「剝皮」 港醫生：降溫都要睇情況","createTime":"2019-06-06T08:39:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T15:50:57.000Z","uid":130626,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0f22da588634c66a6400969e98238b46ad175c6c","tid":1188404,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T08:39:31.000Z","msg":"江蘇南京市的兒童醫院，自上個月來接連收治多名被燙傷的小童，其中3歲的男童銳銳，在家玩耍時絆倒，打翻熱水壺，被開水燙傷，他的祖父急忙為孫兒脫衣時，竟將衣服與皮一同剝下，銳銳送院曾一度休克。香港醫生稱小童燙傷後原則上要先降溫，但要視乎情況，如果衣服與皮膚已經貼在一起，則不要強行脫衣。<br />\n目前仍在南京市兒童醫院留醫的銳銳，入院時情況相當危急。他的母親稱，銳銳在家中玩耍、跑來跑去的時候，被一條電線絆倒，在摔倒時打翻了放在桌上的熱水壺，開水淋在他的身上。當時在家的祖父見狀，想為銳銳把衣服脫掉，但是在脫衣時竟連孫兒皮膚一併撕下來，其母親說：「皮都掉了，嚇死了！」<br />\n家長將銳銳送到醫院，醫生檢查後發現銳銳有15%皮膚被燙傷，入院時一度休克，醫生為他手術清理傷口、植皮，情況才轉趨穩定。<br />\n香港家庭醫生鄭志文稱，每宗燙傷的處理方法不同，但大原則是首先要降溫，如果造成燙傷的物件仍黏在身上，就要先拿走，之後是衣物，如果不是太貼身的衣物，都應該將衣服脫掉，特別是被熱水燙傷，衣服吸了熱水、持續貼在皮膚上，將會造成更大傷害。但脫衣服也要看情況，如果皮膚已與衣服黏在一起，就不要強行脫衣服。<br />\n鄭志文續稱，另一個方法是沖水，如果並非遭不可觸碰水的化學物質燙傷，可以用大量水，連同衣服一同沖洗降溫；降溫後不要亂塗豉油、燙火膏等，應盡快到醫院求醫。<br />\n網民講乜：<br />\n傳說中的3Y ：無知的家長，可憐的孩子！<br />\nqiuqpSSS：痛也要痛了，先降溫！<br />\nLunaMacLeod：老人帶孩子沒辦法照顧的那麼周全&hellip;&hellip;<br />\nIlove一葦航之：值得宣傳一下，我覺得好多人都不知道<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190605/large/1559743332_4aa5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190605%2Flarge%2F1559743332_4aa5.jpg&h=4cbd0753&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190606/59680066\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190606%2F59680066&d=M59wMjr1KB2wSFKn0iQ%2BggwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=9bf21c9a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190606%2F59680066&h=a9ae3db9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190606/59680066</a>"},{"pid":"7eaba6ba39d4903325aa31723e8ea1b2fa402afb","tid":1188404,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T08:43:08.000Z","msg":"睇字都痛<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aed043c384fbd6b08f59ac42b42164758c0d43b","tid":1188404,"uid":4574,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T09:17:22.000Z","msg":"諗起台灣八仙<br />\n用水鎗幫傷者降溫<br />\n沖到成地人皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"827514fe1216d1b21d63ab382f9b5f5685c303a2","tid":1188404,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T09:25:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8867f9337617589f6ce870bdba311089543780a","tid":1188404,"uid":1735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T09:27:07.000Z","msg":"用滾水可唔可以割包皮？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bb7596b50a316dfb848339989a27868e5952818","tid":1188404,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T09:28:52.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"325da5c1583a89c04fa0728a0f0ef21509d8da13","tid":1188404,"uid":4625,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5aed043c384fbd6b08f59ac42b42164758c0d43b","tid":1188404,"uid":4574,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T09:17:22.000Z","msg":"諗起台灣八仙<br />\n用水鎗幫傷者降溫<br />\n沖到成地人皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T09:29:08.000Z","msg":"用水鎗幫傷者降溫點搞到成地人皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6767ef095c5149f44158a814be5fe7340067b302","tid":1188404,"uid":40318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T09:31:45.000Z